so most rangers jump from 17~22% haste to the 40% off hand haste to switch back they'd end up loseing alot of haste dps, so there is a huge chunk of content  ever thing up to farming alot of ntov / or dozer quests that  the rangers best haste is with that off hand weapon, also for grouping the main hand , and alot harder to get epic bit proc's a slow which is great if you don't have a chanter or shaman.<br>
